# NETLIFY DEPLOYMENT INSTRUCTIONS:
# ============================================================================
# 1. Go to: Netlify Dashboard > Your Site > Build & Deploy > Environment
# 2. Add this variable:
#    Key: VITE_API_BASE_URL
#    Value: https://celebrationpoint-backend-production.up.railway.app
# 3. Redeploy your site
# 4. Open browser console and verify:
#    - See "[API CONFIG] âœ… Using API Base URL: https://..."
#    - See "[AXIOS] âœ… Axios instance created successfully"
#
# ============================================================================
# LOCAL DEVELOPMENT INSTRUCTIONS:
# ============================================================================
# 1. Create .env.local (NOT .env.example)
# 2. Set: VITE_API_BASE_URL=http://localhost:8080
# 3. Run: npm run dev
# 4. Check console for configuration logs
#
